{"tid":321414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法官不同意政府有政治動機 否則「為何只針對四人而不針對其他人」","createTime":"2017-07-14T07:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T13:29:55.000Z","uid":48093,"like":3,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"75645bbb3d57444fa874ad09676b28bf09cf7797","tid":321414,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T07:57:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170714/large/1500017959_ae97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170714%2Flarge%2F1500017959_ae97.jpg&h=5c2c1c88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法官區慶祥又於判詞中表示，四名議員要求擱置聆訊的申請亦被撤銷，揚言不認同四人所言，政府DQ議員滲雜政治考慮，又指四人批評政府有「政治動機」純屬揣測，不合邏輯。法官更進一步聲言，若果政府真的有「政治動機」，為何僅申請DQ四人、而未有針對其他被視為「民主派」或非建制派人士。"},{"pid":"5110404bbe741e1423d3a27b32aaba3956c2b1bf","tid":321414,"uid":33848,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T07:58:20.000Z","msg":"乜撚野邏輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a8aceafed695e95605f281c4a8aa331b5cbbff4","tid":321414,"uid":50386,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T08:00:41.000Z","msg":"即係打劫金行淨係搶一條金鍊唔算打劫<br />\n要成間舖清晒先算？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c9f08c0450f3c2eac3dc09582d9a3b0ec8f44d","tid":321414,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T08:00:49.000Z","msg":"好似仲有件建制派要再宣誓"},{"pid":"61db51b73cd4366a9b79c921a293e394066f0006","tid":321414,"uid":17682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T08:02:10.000Z","msg":"個官個腦仲停留響建制/泛民兩派既年代"},{"pid":"490a259a6de06a85302b457859b175b449190a28","tid":321414,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T08:02:19.000Z","msg":"黑人問號"},{"pid":"93b6c904632d4a970b3db022be280e620a312c06","tid":321414,"uid":3342,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T08:04:02.000Z",