news/20060811/20060811015107_0000.html</a>"},{"pid":"aa34ec2250a9194aacfeb816b5a1d5017e741c3b","tid":321414,"uid":7840,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T08:07:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eab5f8d9ce147582f60a10243272429d1ea59377","tid":321414,"uid":60916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T08:07:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170714/large/1500017959_ae97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170714%2Flarge%2F1500017959_ae97.jpg&h=5c2c1c88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法官區慶祥又於判詞中表示，四名議員要求擱置聆訊的申請亦被撤銷，揚言不認同四人所言，政府DQ議員滲雜政治考慮，又指四人批評政府有「政治動機」純屬揣測，不合邏輯。法官更進一步聲言，若果政府真的有「政治動機」，為何僅申請DQ四人、而未有針對其他被視為「民主派」或非建制派人士。</blockquote><br />\n你個法官真係不符邏輯就真"},{"pid":"537317a4c5f134e15341cd460c11aab4f2d82c19","tid":321414,"uid":18679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T08:07:56.000Z","msg":"如果無政治動機就黃定光都搞埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a234bb3dd7dba0832de0dcbb9d105aca0ae90bb","tid":321414,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T08:08:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好似仲有件建制派要再宣誓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哩個應該都要DQ 埋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n到時７７７會話為改善行政立法關係，唔會郁隻共狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"273da513f40ec2b5fc25cb97ef98c5213c7bdd18","tid":321414,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T08:09:05.000Z","msg":"感謝提供笑話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71c7e49bd31fb49be5fceac80c64d9a6ac4aff99","tid":321414,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T08:09:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個仆街法官藍絲底來架<br />\n<br />\n屌佢老母❕‼️<br />\n<br />\n仆街死呀⚠️</blockquote><br />\n深藍到黑底咁，而且離哂地"},{"pid":"e311465ad9d11497aee1ccb76e804f2